items.html: We want to change healthcare — how it’s paid for, delivered, and experienced.

So we’ve gathered together a bunch of smart, big-hearted people from healthcare, tech, retail, and beyond — the kind of people who thrive on challenges that matter. That’s what it means to be Devoted.
Listen, healthcare’s broken. And fixing it? It’s messy work. People say it can’t be done. It’s too big. It’s too much. We say they’re wrong.
Former Chief Technology Officer, Chief Operating Officer, President of Services, Athenahealth
Co-founder of Athenahealth and Castlight Health; former U.S. Chief Technology Officer
Former President at MiniLuxe and Chief People Officer at Athenahealth
Former President of Global Government Affairs and Policy and Global Litigation for GE; veteran law firm and government consulting group leader; former US Senator (MA)
Former Chief Technology Officer of Wayfair and Chief Product Officer/Chief Technology Officer of Athenahealth
Former Vice President of Brand Marketing at Wayfair and veteran of Procter & Gamble, Parthenon/E&Y
Former Chief Operating Officer at Docent Health, Vice President of Product Innovation, Athenahealth
Former Chief Clinical Integration / Network Development Officer, New York Presbyterian
Former Senior Director of Service Operations and Senior Medicare Compliance Officer at Aetna
Former Regional Vice President, Vice President of Provider Development, and Vice President of Florida Primary Care, Humana
Primary Care Physician at Brigham and Women's Hospital; Former Associate Chief Quality Officer at Partners HealthCare
Former Head of Global Healthcare at GIC Private Equity and veteran of BC Partners and Morgan Stanley
Partner at Venrock; Adjunct Professor at Stanford; Former Special Assistant to President Obama; Former Partner at McKinsey
21st US Secretary of Health and Human Services; 44th Governor of Kansas; CEO of Sebelius Resources
Former U.S. Senate Majority Leader representing TN; Founder of Vanderbilt Multi-Organ Transplant Center; Chairman of Executives Council of Cressey & Co
General Partner at Andreessen Horowitz; Founder of a16z BioHealth; Former Professor at Stanford University
Co-founder and Partner at Uprising; Partner at The Space Between; Co-founder and Managing Director at Global Asset Capital
Former President of Healthcare Services at Humana; Managing member of Perkins, Smith, and Associates
Co-founder and CEO of Devoted Health; Former CTO, COO, and President, Athenahealth
Co-founder and Chairman of Devoted Health; Former US Chief Technology Officer and Assistant to the President; Co-founder of Athenahealth and Castlight Health
Senior Fellow, Harvard’s Belfer Center; Former U.S. Chief Data Scientist; Former Head of Data Products, Chief Scientist , and Chief Security Officer, LinkedIn
North Carolina and South Carolina Market President
30+ years of executive experience with Medicare Advantage. Launched and ran de novo Medicare Advantage plans in multiple states across the southeast for the 2 largest national MA carriers.
30+ years in executive healthcare leadership. Launched Medicare Advantage product for a large regional plan in Ohio. Licensed attorney with experience in healthcare, insurance and employee benefits.

35+ years in executive leadership. Started a Medicare Advantage company that sold to Blue Cross Blue Shield of Arizona. Founder of a physician global risk IPA that sold to Davita and a primary care group that's now part of VillageMD.

17+ years of experience in Medicare Advantage with national payers. Led an all-in one primary care physician practice. Started and managed multiple independent physician associations, primarily in the southeast.

19+ years as senior executive leader for multiple health plans with Cigna-Healthspring. Prior experience leading key strategic health system relationships with multiple systems. Certified executive coach.
13+ years of experience, including senior leadership roles at regional and national Medicare Advantage health plans. Engineer by training.
10+ years with a national provider group advocating for access to care for over 100k seniors. Previous healthcare experience at national payers.
20 years of experience in senior leadership roles at Universal American Corporation. 5 years at Miami Children’s Hospital.
We’re in this for the long haul. We want to work with people we love for a cause we believe in. Life is short.

Devoted Health Guides are here 8am to 8pm, 7 days a week.
Or call us at 1-800-DEVOTED (338–6833) TTY 711
